To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private PercentagePriceOscillator _ppo;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_ppo = PPO(symbol, fastPeriod, slowPeriod, movingAverageType);

// In OnData()
if (_ppo.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "fast", _ppo.Fast.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "slow", _ppo.Slow.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "signal", _ppo.Signal.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "histogram", _ppo.Histogram.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "percentagepriceoscillator", _ppo.Current.Value);
}
